name: MiloManara-768
description: Embedding inspired by Milo Manara, an Italian comic book writer and artist.

modelVersions.name: V3
modelVersions.description:
Improved version made mixing milomanara-768 V1 + V2 (not published).

It works very well with a simple prompt like "portrait of a girl, art by milomanara-768-v3" but feel free to experiment with more complex prompts.
